---
<section id="contact" class="bg-ink border-t border-paper-dark">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 md:py-32">

    <p class="font-body text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-12" style="color: var(--color-ink-muted);">
      Let's talk
    </p>

    <h2
      class="font-display font-light mb-8"
      style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem); line-height: var(--leading-tight); color: var(--color-paper); max-width: 18ch;"
    >
      If you've made it here, you've seen how I think.
    </h2>

    <p class="font-body text-lg mb-16" style="color: var(--color-ink-muted); max-width: 52ch; line-height: var(--leading-normal);">
      I'm looking for a team that ships things and cares about how —
      somewhere with enough structure to learn from and enough ambition to keep moving.
      If that's you, or you know someone, I'd like to talk.
    </p>

    <a
      href="mailto:wency19valentin@gmail.com"
      class="inline-block font-body text-base transition-colors"
      style="color: var(--color-accent);"
      onmouseover="this.style.color='var(--color-accent-warm)'"
      onmouseout="this.style.color='var(--color-accent)'"
    >
      wency19valentin@gmail.com →
    </a>

    <div class="mt-24 pt-8 border-t" style="border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);">
      <p class="font-body text-xs" style="color: var(--color-ink-muted);">
        Built with Astro, Tailwind, and deliberate AI use. ·
        <a href="https://github.com/lukahristic/portfolio" class="hover:text-accent transition-colors" style="color: var(--color-ink-muted);">
          Source
        </a>
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
